<div class="title">Vasoconstriction</div>
<div class="substance">Methylone (bk-MDMA) & 2C-E</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=chloric_icon&Exact=1">chloric_icon</a></div>


